            <title>1.6.4</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:11:57 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>20</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Return to launcher screen automatically when the Claude process exits unexpectedly, instead of showing a static error message that required manual navigation
- Detect and handle CLI subprocess death (e.g., killed by another agent) even when the Node.js shim remains alive
- Clean up orphaned child processes when the shim process is terminated externally
]]></description>
